{"tid":447190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港日式偶像團體_01","createTime":"2017-10-25T05:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T10:08:42.000Z","uid":147408,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2763633315e3d2f351f652652d331457b8c865ad","tid":447190,"uid":147408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:15:14.000Z","msg":"今次介紹一個香港日式偶像團體<strong>Ariel Project</strong>（<strong>アリエルプロジェクト</strong>），她們由六個香港女仔組成，包括寶藍色擔當<strong>Aoi</strong>、橙色擔當<strong>Hinako</strong>、白色擔當<strong>Nanami</strong>、玫瑰粉紅色擔當<strong>Senia</strong>、綠色擔當<strong>Midori</strong>同埋粉紅色擔當<strong>Yura</strong>。她們主要走日系偶像路線,所以表演主要以日文歌為主, 她們有如人魚一樣動人的歌聲,令台下觀眾深深被她們的表演吸引,舞蹈方面也是日系偶像風格,她們用日文作出自我介紹及Catch Phrase,增加互動性,同台下觀眾打成一片。<br />\n她們成立差不多兩年,已經去了不同地方表演,包括上海、廣州、東京及台灣,同場有不少日本偶像團體,她們透過互相交流及同台表演,吸收其他隊伍的長處,來增進她們的表演實力,令到台上表演更加精彩。上年同今年Ariel Project成員都出席了一個叫<strong>@JAM</strong>日本大型偶像event, 這個event是日本每年一度大型活動,同場有<strong>欅坂46</strong>及<strong>AKB48 Team 8</strong>等為人所認識的偶像團體,她們透過舞台表演及物販時段,令日本觀眾更加認識到她們的魅力所在。<br />\n她們除了會出席海外表演外,以香港為基地的她們,每個月會有定期表演,如果大家有興趣了解她們,歡迎去現場感受她們表演魅力,10月28日是<strong>Aoi</strong>生誕祭,到時她會有solo曲,希望大家可以到現場應援她,到時生誕委員會提供應援物,到時麻煩依照委員會人士指示去應援她, 。另外她們不斷有表演活動,包括本地同海外,18-19/11會是<strong>Nanami</strong> 及<strong>Yura</strong>生誕祭,其中<strong>Yura</strong>生誕祭可以透過特別途徑獲得票價減免,有興趣人士去觀看她們表演就不要錯過這個機會!!<br />\n<br />\nYura生誕祭預約link: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/bAQ4wy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbAQ4wy&d=HeJvc9wm17QykqK%2Be%2FRS0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=657e3ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/bAQ4wy</a><br />\nAoi生誕祭預約link: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfCNWoRVx7fH5YmZFg9GknCL3mJgj9_MZWNjnf6sj4qJcSFnQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfCNWoRVx7fH5YmZFg9GknCL3mJgj9_MZWNjnf6sj4qJcSFnQ%2Fviewform&d=HeJvc9wm17QykqK%2Be%2FRS0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0fd7e460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfCNWoRVx7fH5YmZFg9GknCL3mJgj9_MZWNjnf6sj4qJcSFnQ/viewform</a><br />\nNanami生誕祭預約link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfPsa8bHZVVKWrfcc0b6iazzWkligPu44PVkCmuGtgi0AziTw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfPsa8bHZVVKWrfcc0b6iazzWkligPu44PVkCmuGtgi0AziTw%2Fviewform&d=HeJvc9wm17QykqK%2Be%2FRS0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=670e9115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfPsa8bHZVVKWrfcc0b6iazzWkligPu44PVkCmuGtgi0AziTw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n她們有隊伍FB專頁及twitter,另外她們會用showroom做直播,大家可以入來跟她們互動及聊天<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131342_f2737092408fae7e0595cd3c9b070c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131342_f2737092408fae7e0595cd3c9b070c51.jpg&h=7229a18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131342_087f7359063091caa2405402653eac3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131342_087f7359063091caa2405402653eac3b.jpg&h=bb67453e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131343_d4ede8fbe700c833eec6010472660be4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131343_d4ede8fbe700c833eec6010472660be4.jpg&h=3960276e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131343_245082dd9c4325d95a9de0b9040b4568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131343_245082dd9c4325d95a9de0b9040b4568.jpg&h=b0836ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131343_caa9eea8d7a336dd23fda5a6532cd177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131343_caa9eea8d7a336dd23fda5a6532cd177.jpg&h=1711619e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131343_011268e3fa32a71d10c3ab68a9681787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131343_011268e3fa32a71d10c3ab68a9681787.jpg&h=c0b4fb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131343_bb525ee8de659bf216bd41ece19d3f2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131343_bb525ee8de659bf216bd41ece19d3f2f.jpg&h=ba572df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131344_6d1028df468e6965d35460648f8ae193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131344_6d1028df468e6965d35460648f8ae193.jpg&h=941ba034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131344_5fc9daaea667819f9cfb2f29586ec1f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131344_5fc9daaea667819f9cfb2f29586ec1f9.jpg&h=a9e1dbdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/131344_fbcffbd8f327a17a610058d4bf9d8476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F131344_fbcffbd8f327a17a610058d4bf9d8476.jpg&h=73a7e398&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d4ee14cacb862001f4ecc08c54b8c5a39c50dc","tid":447190,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f380fd39aae89909a2f98f4721c78d6dfcddbc1","tid":447190,"uid":91744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T20:03:06.000Z","msg":"咁醜樣都可以做偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狗也不屌 由其係個aoi豬到閪咁成個男人樣 邊忽靚<img src=\"/ass